[normal]11[bold]).[bold] [bold]Berner
[normal] and 
[normal]Kothvala
[normal] (2001) through a series of studies beginning in 1991, 1994 and culminating with 
[normal]Geocarb
[normal] III have documented the CO2 content of the atmosphere throughout the 
[normal]Phanerozoic
[normal].
[normal](see also 
[normal]Berner
