[normal]  The study shows very high values throughout the Paleozoic,
[normal] (541 – 250 million years ago)
[normal] and the validity of the 
[normal]very 
[normal]high atmospheric CO2
[normal] values
[normal] is corroborated f
[normal]rom individual 
[normal]palaesol
[normal] analyses
